1
Humanism for Sale, Bibliography, 9/14/08
Bibliography
The literature on education and printing history is immense. Below are listed only
the books and articles cited as sources for Humanism for Sale. For the non-specialist
reader the most useful general studies in English are Grafton and Jardine 1986, Grendler
1989, and Black 2001.
